    <p>This is the third project in a small family. The first is my <a href="https://www.thingelstad.com">blog</a>, which I have been writing for over twenty years. The second is the <a href="https://weekly.thingelstad.com">Weekly Thing</a>, a newsletter I have been publishing since 2017. Another Thing is the audio counterpart, and the format I am still figuring out.</p>

    <h2>About Jamie</h2>
    <p>Jamie Thingelstad is the host. He works in technology and has spent a long time writing on the web.</p>

    <h2>How often do new episodes come out?</h2>
